videos.headline: Stewart hits difficult step-back jumper
videos.description: Breanna Stewart gets the ball at the free throw line and hits the step-back shot right in her defender's face early.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Stewart hits difficult step-back jumper) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bird hits Howard with no-look full-court pass
videos.description: Sue Bird throws the ball the length of the court for the no-look pass to Natasha Howard who hits the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Bird hits Howard with no-look full-court pass) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Storm hit back-to-back buckets to take 19-point lead
videos.description: Breanna Stewart and Jewell Loyd hit back-to-back buckets as the Storm take a stunning 19-point lead over the Aces.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Storm hit back-to-back buckets to take 19-point lead) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Storm win 2020 WNBA Finals in 33-point rout of Aces
videos.description: The Storm celebrate their 2020 WNBA Finals win with a dominating Game 3 victory over the Las Vegas Aces.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Storm win 2020 WNBA Finals in 33-point rout of Aces) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bird hoists WNBA Finals trophy as Storm celebrate 4th championship win
videos.description: WNBA commissioner Cathy Engelbert awards the 2020 WNBA Finals trophy to Sue Bird and the Seattle Storm.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Bird hoists WNBA Finals trophy as Storm celebrate 4th championship win) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jewell Loyd gives thanks to Kobe Bryant after Storm secure WNBA title
videos.description: Jewell Loyd gets emotional and dedicates the Storm's WNBA Finals win over the Aces to Kobe Bryant.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Jewell Loyd gives thanks to Kobe Bryant after Storm secure WNBA title) 2020/10/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stewart fuels Storm's WNBA championship win
videos.description: 2020 WNBA Finals MVP Breanna Stewart dominates Game 3 vs. the Aces with a masterful 26-point performance, hitting 10 of 14 shots in the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Highlight (Stewart fuels Storm's WNBA championship win) 2020/10/6 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Stewart discusses winning WNBA Finals MVP following 2019 injury
videos.description: Breanna Stewart explains what it means to bounce back from her 2019 Achilles injury to win her second WNBA title and MVP.

tracking.trackingName: COM_WNBA Interview (Stewart discusses winning WNBA Finals MVP following 2019 injury) 2020/10/6 ESHEET
